the University of Illinois at Chicago in 1974 and an MBA fromthe University of Chicago Booth School of BusinessExecutive Program in 1986.                    UIC Logo        Engineering Alumni       Contact   851 S. Morgan - SEO Rm. 811  Phone: 3129969422  MWilli60@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 